    <tr>
      <td style="vertical-align: top;">
      <h1 style="text-align: center;"><big><b><b>Dvonn</b></b> </big></h1>
Dvonn is
a stacking game where the number of stacks, and the mobility of the
remaining stacks, is continously declining.&nbsp; Like the other games
in the Gipf series, it can be a real brain-burner - but it can also be
played pretty casually.<br>
      <br>
      <span style="font-weight: bold;">Robots:</span>&nbsp; Duimbot
seems to be about right against beginners.&nbsp;&nbsp; Smartbot and
Bestbot were originally not much better, but their new, upgraded
versions ought to be more challenging.<br>
      <br>
      </td>
      <td style="vertical-align: top;"><img
 style="width: 523px; height: 234px;" alt="dvonn board"
 src="../images/dvonn-small.jpg"><br>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
