<span style="font-weight: bold;"><br>
The back story: </span>Dvonn was a tossup (with Yinsh) to be the
second Gipf game at boardspace.&nbsp; Given my long term plan to have
all the Gipf games, it had to be added eventually.&nbsp; So when other
stacking games were being added, Dvonn finally became the current
project.<br>
